South Africa’s IDC to Increase Investment in Tourism, Business Report Says

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-05-10T06:26:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/south-africa-s-idc-to-boost-investment-in-tourism-business-report-says.html
South Africa ’s Industrial
Develoipment Corp. plans to spend 1.8 billion rand on tourism
projects over the next five years, Business Report said, citing
Christine Engelbrecht, head of the IDC’s tourism business unit.  The state lender invested 249 million in tourism in its
last financial year, the Johannesburg-based newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
